  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&#x201C;Med Media&#x201D;: Working Towards Media Sector Reform in the Southern Mediterranean Region (ENPI)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The declared objective of this tender is to support the development of a more public service-orientated media landscape in the southern Mediterranean countries. This new initiative will focus on decision-makers and media leaders as opposed to rank-and-file journalists. It will work to facilitate institutional and legal reforms in the media sector by building capacity within this target group and providing up-to-date research on the state of the industry.</narrative>
  </description>
